_ _7"></span>表面上看来，<span class="_ _19"></span>《心经》<span class="_ _8"></span>、<span class="_ _19"></span>《金刚经》<span class="_ _8"></span>、<span class="_ _19"></span>《地</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y24d ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">藏经》<span class="_ _4"></span>的文字不是很多，<span class="_ _6"></span>但它里面的甚深涵义，<span class="_ _4"></span>很多人穷尽</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y24e ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">一生绞尽脑汁也难以领悟。 </div><div class="t m0 x23 h4 y24f ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls39 ws0">也许有些人会问：<span class="_ _8"></span><span class="ls40">“佛教如果真有这么好，为什么很多</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y250 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">人都不信？”<span class="_ _b"></span>其实，<span class="_ _b"></span>任何一种高深的学问，<span class="_ _b"></span>不管是科学知识，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y251 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">还是佛教道理，<span class="_ _5"></span>能接受的人肯定只是少数，<span class="_ _4"></span>不可能人人都完</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y252 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">全明白。<span class="_ _d"></span><span class="ls28">就像懂得珍宝价值的人，<span class="_ _d"></span><span class="ls0">在世间上也是如凤毛麟角，</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y253 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">一般人很难分清真伪——不过，如今信佛的人也为数不少，</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
